sections.text:
38-2846.Temporary educational permit, defined.

Temporary educational permit means a permit to practice pharmacy in a supervised educational program approved by the board.

SourceLaws 1978, LB 675, § 2;Laws 1999, LB 828, § 115;R.S.1943, (2003), § 71-1,147.18;Laws 2007, LB463, § 942.
